[ Basic Inform test case code ]
[ File: BIP-SayName.txt ]
[ URL: https://github.com/ganelson/inform/tree/master/inform7/Tests/Test%20Basic ]

The planet Mars is an object.
The asteroid Ceres is an object.

To begin:
	showme Mars;
	say "Look! It's [Mars]. Yes, [the planet Mars]; not just [a Mars]. [The Mars]. [A Mars]? Nope.";
	showme Ceres;
	say "Look! It's [Ceres]. Yes, [the asteroid Ceres]; not just [a Ceres], or [an asteroid]. [The Ceres]. [A Ceres]? Nope. [An asteroid]? Seriously not.";